Value device (\S+)
Value current (\d+)
Value range (.+)
Value danger (\d+)
Value thresh (\d+)
Value status (.*)

Start
  ^Chassis/Device\s*\|?\s*Current\s*\|?\s*Range\s*\|?\s*Danger\s*\|?\s*Thresh\s*\|?\s*Status\s*$$
  ^[-+|]+\s*$$ -> Data

Data
  ^\s*${device}\s+${current}\s+${range}\s+${danger}\s+${thresh}\s+${status}\s*$$
